{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":948,"text":"Joan Blades: Do you have\npolitically diverse friends?"},{"time":3925,"text":"What do you talk about with them?"},{"time":6076,"text":"I'm a progressive; I live\nin a town full of progressives,"},{"time":8930,"text":"and 15 years ago, I didn't have\nany conservative friends."},{"time":12602,"text":"Now I have a wonderful mix of friends,"},{"time":15390,"text":"and they include John."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17354,"text":"John Gable: I am not a progressive."},{"time":19672,"text":"I'm a Republican who grew up\nin a Republican family"},{"time":22575,"text":"in the conservative South,"},{"time":23880,"text":"and even worked in Republican politics,\nlocally and at the national level."},{"time":27584,"text":"But the last 24 years,\nI've been in technology"},{"time":30156,"text":"and living in a very progressive area."},{"time":32483,"text":"So I have a lot of progressive friends,"},{"time":34407,"text":"including Joan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36666,"text":"JB: I was born in Berkeley, California,"},{"time":39194,"text":"a notoriously progressive college town."},{"time":42299,"text":"And I live there now."},{"time":44891,"text":"In 1998, six months into the Monica\nLewinsky-Clinton impeachment scandal,"},{"time":50614,"text":"I helped cofound MoveOn.org\nwith a one-sentence petition:"},{"time":55195,"text":"\"Congress must immediately\ncensure the president"},{"time":58526,"text":"and move on to pressing issues\nfacing the nation.\""},{"time":61507,"text":"Now, that was actually\na very unifying petition in many ways."},{"time":65107,"text":"You could love Clinton or hate Clinton"},{"time":67349,"text":"and agree that the best thing\nfor the country was to move on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71858,"text":"As the leader of MoveOn,\nI saw the polarization just continue."},{"time":76457,"text":"And I found myself wondering"},{"time":79557,"text":"why I saw things so differently"},{"time":82064,"text":"than many people\nin other parts of the country."},{"time":84765,"text":"So in 2005, when I had an opportunity\nto get together with grassroots leaders"},{"time":90995,"text":"across the political divide,"},{"time":93226,"text":"I grabbed it."},{"time":95144,"text":"And I became friends with a lot of people"},{"time":97874,"text":"I never had a chance to talk to before."},{"time":101050,"text":"And that included leadership\nin the Christian Coalition,"},{"time":104348,"text":"often seen as on the right\nthe way MoveOn is seen as on the left."},{"time":108797,"text":"And this lead to me\nshowing up on Capitol Hill"},{"time":112168,"text":"with one of the Christian Coalition\nleaders, my friend,"},{"time":116456,"text":"to lobby for net neutrality."},{"time":118452,"text":"That was powerful."},{"time":119627,"text":"We turned heads."},{"time":121915,"text":"So this work was transformational for me."},{"time":125997,"text":"And I found myself wondering:"},{"time":128401,"text":"How could vast numbers of people\nhave the opportunity"},{"time":132266,"text":"to really connect with people\nthat have very different views?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136972,"text":"JG: I was born Oneida, Tennessee,"},{"time":139013,"text":"right across the state border\nfrom a small coal mining town,"},{"time":143699,"text":"Stearns, Kentucky."},{"time":145040,"text":"And I lived there\nfor the first few years of my life,"},{"time":147580,"text":"before moving to another small town,\nFrankfort, Kentucky."},{"time":150348,"text":"Basically, I grew up\nin small-town America,"},{"time":152472,"text":"conservative at its heart."},{"time":154908,"text":"Now, Stearns and Berkeley --\nthey're a little different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158598,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161543,"text":"So in the '90s I moved out west\nto a progressive area"},{"time":165179,"text":"to work in technology --"},{"time":166730,"text":"worked at Microsoft, worked at Netscape."},{"time":168826,"text":"I actually became the product manager lead\nfor Netscape Navigator,"},{"time":172039,"text":"the first popular web browser."},{"time":174204,"text":"Now in the early days of the internet,"},{"time":176119,"text":"we were just moved\nand inspired by a vision:"},{"time":179319,"text":"when we're connected to all\nthese different people around the world"},{"time":182590,"text":"and all these different ideas,"},{"time":184132,"text":"we'll be able to make great decisions,"},{"time":185982,"text":"and we'll be able to appreciate each other"},{"time":188026,"text":"for the beautiful diversity\nthat the whole world has to offer."},{"time":191019,"text":"Now I also, 20 years ago, gave a speech"},{"time":192956,"text":"saying it might not work out that way,"},{"time":195645,"text":"that we might actually be trained\nto discriminate against each other"},{"time":199354,"text":"in new ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202357,"text":"So what happened?"},{"time":204233,"text":"It's not like we just woke up one day\nand decided to hate each other more."},{"time":208532,"text":"Here's what happened."},{"time":210249,"text":"There's just too much noise --\ntoo many people, too many ideas --"},{"time":213385,"text":"so we use technology\nto filter it out a little bit."},{"time":215921,"text":"And what happens?"},{"time":217417,"text":"It lets in ideas I already agree with."},{"time":220080,"text":"It lets in the popular ideas,"},{"time":222016,"text":"it lets in people just like me\nwho think just like me."},{"time":224834,"text":"That sounds kind of good, right?"},{"time":226911,"text":"Well, not necessarily,"},{"time":229091,"text":"because two very scary things happen"},{"time":232038,"text":"when we have such narrow worldviews."},{"time":234902,"text":"First, we become more extreme\nin our beliefs."},{"time":239272,"text":"Second, we become less tolerant\nof anybody who's different than we are."},{"time":246266,"text":"Does this sound familiar?"},{"time":248856,"text":"Does this sound like modern America?\nThe modern world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252365,"text":"Well, the good news is\nthat technology is changing,"},{"time":254852,"text":"and it could change for the better."},{"time":256562,"text":"And that's, in fact,\nwhy I started AllSides.com --"},{"time":259023,"text":"to create technologies and services\nto free us from these filter bubbles."},{"time":263381,"text":"The very first thing we did was create\ntechnology that identifies bias,"},{"time":266977,"text":"so we could show different\nperspectives side by side"},{"time":270246,"text":"to free us from the filter\nbubbles of news media."},{"time":274193,"text":"And then I met Joan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277291,"text":"JB: So I met John outside\nof Washington, DC,"},{"time":280684,"text":"with an idealistic group\nof cross-partisan bridge builders,"},{"time":286482,"text":"and we wanted to re-weave\nthe fabric of our communities."},{"time":290109,"text":"We believe that our differences\ncan be a strength,"},{"time":294534,"text":"that our values can be complimentary"},{"time":297417,"text":"and that we have to overcome the fight"},{"time":300392,"text":"so that we can honor everyone's values"},{"time":302912,"text":"and not lose any of our own."},{"time":305051,"text":"I went for this wonderful walk with John,"},{"time":307105,"text":"where I started learning\nabout the work he was doing"},{"time":309625,"text":"to pierce the filter bubble."},{"time":311756,"text":"It was powerful;"},{"time":313117,"text":"it was brilliant."},{"time":315137,"text":"Living in separate narratives is not good."},{"time":318907,"text":"We can't even have a conversation\nor do collaborative problem-solving"},{"time":322792,"text":"when we don't share the same facts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326605,"text":"JG: So one thing you take away from today"},{"time":328607,"text":"is if Joan Blades asks you\nto go on a walk,"},{"time":331001,"text":"go on that walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332311,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333968,"text":"It changed things. It really changed\nthe way I was thinking about things."},{"time":337488,"text":"To free ourselves from the filter bubbles,"},{"time":339606,"text":"we can't just think about\ninformation filter bubbles,"},{"time":342170,"text":"but also relationship\nand social filter bubbles."},{"time":344882,"text":"You see, we human beings -- we're not\nnearly as smart as we think we are."},{"time":348366,"text":"We don't generally make\ndecisions intellectually."},{"time":350847,"text":"We make them emotionally, intuitively,"},{"time":352778,"text":"and then we use our big old brains"},{"time":354523,"text":"to rationalize anything\nwe want to rationalize."},{"time":356961,"text":"We're not really like Vulcans\nlike Mr. Spock,"},{"time":360400,"text":"we're more like bold cowboys\nlike Captain Kirk,"},{"time":363786,"text":"or passionate idealists like Dr. McCoy."},{"time":367504,"text":"OK, for those of y'all who prefer\nthe new \"Star Trek\" crew,"},{"time":370417,"text":"here you go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371593,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372633,"text":"JB: Don't forget the strong women!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374863,"text":"JG: Come on, strong women. OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376350,"text":"JB: All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377551,"text":"John and I are both \"Star Trek\" fans."},{"time":379408,"text":"What's not to love about a future\nwith that kind of optimism?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":384495,"text":"JG: And having a good future in mind\nis a big deal -- very important."},{"time":388142,"text":"And understanding what the problem is\nis very important."},{"time":390914,"text":"But we have to do something."},{"time":392316,"text":"So what do we do?"},{"time":393523,"text":"It's actually not that hard."},{"time":394897,"text":"We have to add diversity to our lives --"},{"time":396932,"text":"not just information,\nbut relationship diversity."},{"time":400273,"text":"And by diversity,\nI mean big \"D\" diversity,"},{"time":402988,"text":"not just racial and gender,\nwhich are very important,"},{"time":405877,"text":"but also ..."},{"time":407820,"text":"diversity of age, like young and old;"},{"time":410564,"text":"rural and urban;"},{"time":412787,"text":"liberal and conservative;"},{"time":415428,"text":"in the US, Democrat and Republican."},{"time":418418,"text":"Now, one of the great examples\nof somebody freeing themselves"},{"time":421674,"text":"from their filter bubbles"},{"time":422941,"text":"and getting a more diverse life"},{"time":424578,"text":"is, once again, next to me -- Joan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427551,"text":"JB: So the question is:"},{"time":429388,"text":"Who among you has had\nrelationships lost or harmed"},{"time":433878,"text":"due to differences in politics,\nreligion or whatever?"},{"time":437484,"text":"Raise your hands."},{"time":439950,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":441132,"text":"This year I have talked to so many people"},{"time":443929,"text":"that have experienced that kind of loss."},{"time":449487,"text":"I've seen tears well up in people's eyes\nas they talk about family members"},{"time":453824,"text":"from whom they're estranged."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456166,"text":"Living Room Conversations were designed"},{"time":459888,"text":"to begin to heal political\nand personal differences."},{"time":465891,"text":"They're simple conversations"},{"time":467627,"text":"where two friends with different\nviewpoints each invite two friends"},{"time":472274,"text":"for structured conversation,"},{"time":473914,"text":"where everyone's agreed\nto some simple ground rules:"},{"time":476970,"text":"curiosity, listening,\nrespect, taking turns --"},{"time":480083,"text":"everything we learned\nin kindergarten, right?"},{"time":482215,"text":"Really easy."},{"time":484017,"text":"So by the time you're talking about\nthe topic you've agreed to talk about,"},{"time":488907,"text":"you actually have the sense that,"},{"time":490572,"text":"\"You know, I kind of like this person,\""},{"time":492546,"text":"and you listen to each other differently."},{"time":494886,"text":"That's kind of a human condition;"},{"time":496504,"text":"we listen differently\nto people we care about."},{"time":499159,"text":"And then there's reflection"},{"time":501820,"text":"and possibly next steps."},{"time":504301,"text":"This is a deep listening practice;"},{"time":506964,"text":"it's never a debate."},{"time":509172,"text":"And that's incredibly powerful."},{"time":511366,"text":"These conversations\nin our own living rooms"},{"time":515704,"text":"with people who have different viewpoints"},{"time":518421,"text":"are an incredible adventure."},{"time":520461,"text":"We rediscover that we can respect\nand even love people"},{"time":523904,"text":"that are different from us."},{"time":526148,"text":"And it's powerful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529014,"text":"JG: So, what are you curious about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532061,"text":"JB: What's the conversation\nyou yearn to have?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535199,"text":"JG: Let's do this together."},{"time":537177,"text":"Together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538698,"text":"JB: Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539873,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540920,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":543134,"text":"JB and JG: Thank you."}]}]}